    <Node ToolID="294">
      <GuiSettings Plugin="AlteryxGuiToolkit.TextBox.TextBox">
        <Position x="92" y="234" width="1018" height="360" />
      </GuiSettings>
      <Properties>
        <Configuration>
          <Text>Preparation: You have to set up the LLM Override tool(which is on right side) before running the workflow and configure the LLM model you want to use. A fast model is recommended.

Note: LLM may not always return perfect answers. Because it is primarily tuned for Gemini (2.5 flash), using other LLM models may result in unintended behavior.

If you do not want to use LLM: Enable the Detour tool (Tool ID 276).

If you encounter the following error, you have hit the LLM rate limit. Please limit the number of workflows you process at once.
"Warning: Prompt (279): Error occurred in LLM response generation: 429 Client Error: Too Many Requests for url: https://us1.alteryxcloud.com/aims/v1/generatedContent"

The GenAI tool may also shows an error if the workflow file is too large. In this case, you should either change the model or review the LLM agreement.</Text>
          <Font name="メイリオ" size="9.75" style="0" />
          <TextColor name="Black" />
          <FillColor name="White" />
          <Shape shape="3" />
          <Justification Justification="3" />
        </Configuration>
        <Annotation DisplayMode="0">
          <Name />
          <DefaultAnnotationText />
          <Left value="False" />
        </Annotation>
      </Properties>
    </Node>
